  "content": "Scenario: Senior-to-senior support and community building\n    Given Margaret is in \"younger\" senior cohort (65-74)\n    And older seniors (75+) need support and connection\n    When the community_elohim coordinates senior support\n    Then Margaret should be part of senior mutual aid networks\n    And her peer support should be recognized as care contribution\n    And senior-to-senior care should prevent isolation\n    And age-matched support should be valued alongside intergenerational\n    And senior community should be strengthened through care economy\n    And Margaret should build relationships with peers\n",
